Version 8.0 Darwin
Added:
- Support old packages without compatibility layer
- Automatic triggers for mpkg-base packages
 - Initsh
 - OSXSubstrate
 - Etc.
- Able to select multiple packages
- More in security patches
- Verifies broken package

